---
// Message — personal love letter from fiancé to fiancée, 10th anniversary
---

<section class="py-28 px-6 sm:px-12 md:px-20 lg:px-28 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative deco -->
  <div class="absolute top-8 left-8 text-5xl animate-drift select-none pointer-events-none opacity-25">🌸</div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 right-8 text-5xl animate-float-slow select-none pointer-events-none opacity-25">🌺</div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-4 text-3xl animate-sparkle select-none pointer-events-none opacity-15">💕</div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-4 text-3xl animate-sparkle select-none pointer-events-none opacity-15">✨</div>

  <div class="max-w-2xl xl:max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
    <!-- Eyebrow -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-10 reveal">
      <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-[var(--pink-hot)]/30"></div>
    <span class="font-hand text-[var(--pink-hot)] text-2xl px-4">a letter from Cabz 💌</span>
      <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-[var(--pink-hot)]/30"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Opening quote -->
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="font-display text-[7rem] leading-none text-[var(--pink-hot)]/15 select-none block -mb-8">"</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Letter card -->
    <div class="card p-8 md:p-12 reveal reveal-delay-1 text-left">
      <p class="font-hand text-[var(--text-muted)] text-xl mb-5">My dearest Babz,</p>

      <p class="font-display text-[clamp(1.05rem,2.2vw,1.35rem)] text-[var(--text-dark)] leading-relaxed italic mb-5">
        Ten years. <span class="text-gradient-pink not-italic font-bold">Ten beautiful, imperfect, unforgettable years.</span>
        And here you are, turning 28, more radiant than ever, and somehow even more mine.
      </p>
      <p class="font-sans text-[var(--text-mid)] text-base leading-relaxed mb-5">
        I’ve had a front-row seat to everything you’ve become. The late nights, the breakthroughs,
        the quiet victories you never made a big deal of. I’ve watched you grow into the most
        extraordinary woman, not just someone I love, but someone I deeply admire every single day.
        Watching you bloom has been one of the greatest privileges of my life.
      </p>
      <p class="font-sans text-[var(--text-mid)] text-base leading-relaxed mb-5">
        This past year gave us something I will carry with me forever. You said <em>yes</em>.
        In that one single moment, every year before it suddenly made perfect sense. Every argument
        we survived, every distance we closed, every ordinary Tuesday we spent together, it all
        pointed here. To you. To us. You are my home, my adventure, my greatest joy. My fiancée.
        My forever.
      </p>
      <p class="font-sans text-[var(--text-mid)] text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
        On your 28th birthday, I need you to know: you are deeply loved, endlessly celebrated,
        and fiercely chosen, today and every single day that follows.
      </p>

      <p class="font-display text-[clamp(1rem,2vw,1.3rem)] text-gradient-pink italic mb-8">
        Here's to 28. Here's to us. Here's to forever. 💍
      </p>
      <!-- Sign-off -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-2">
        <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-[var(--pink-hot)]/20"></div>
        <p class="font-script text-[var(--pink-hot)] text-2xl whitespace-nowrap">Always yours, Cabz 💜</p>
        <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-[var(--pink-hot)]/20"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Closing quote -->
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <span class="font-display text-[7rem] leading-none text-berry-500/10 select-none block -mt-8 text-right">"</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Sticker row -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-2 flex-wrap reveal reveal-delay-3">
      {['🌸 28th birthday', '💍 fiancée', '✨ 10 years', '💕 forever'].map(s => (
        <span class="sticker text-[var(--pink-hot)] border-[var(--pink-hot)]/60 bg-[#fff0f4] text-lg">
          {s}
        </span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .banat-note {
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 16px 14px 20px;
    border-left: 4px solid;
  }
  .banat-pink     { background: #fff0f4; border-color: var(--pink-hot); }
  .banat-lavender { background: #f0ecff; border-color: #9c27b0; }
  .banat-yellow   { background: #fffce8; border-color: #d97706; }
  .banat-green    { background: #f0fdf4; border-color: #16a34a; }
  .banat-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
</style>